# EventType: 14542008
#
# Descriptor: [B_c+ -> (J/psi(1S) -> mu+ mu-) (tau+ -> pi+ pi+ pi- pi0 nu_tau~) nu_tau]CC
#
# NickName: Bc_JpsiTauNu,pipipipi0nu=DecProdCut,BcVegPy,taulababar_Update
#
# Cuts:  BcDaughtersInLHCb 
#
# Production: BcVegPy
#
# Documentation: Bc decay to J/psi and tau using BcVegPy dedicated model
# tau decay to 3 charged and one neutral pions using the Tauola with BaBar configuration.
# The 14542005 file is wrongly configured with TAUOLA 6, which causes the tau->inclusive but not 3pipi0.
# We update it here.
# EndDocumentation
# 
# PhysicsWG: B2SL
#
# CPUTime: < 1 min
