#
#
# Tauola steering options
Define TauolaCurrentOption 1 
Define TauolaBR1 1.0
#
Alias         MyTau+   tau+
Alias         MyTau-   tau-
ChargeConj    MyTau+   MyTau-
#
Alias       MyJpsi  J/psi
ChargeConj  MyJpsi  MyJpsi
#
#
#
Decay B_c+sig
  1.00000 MyJpsi MyTau+  nu_tau PHOTOS BC_VMN 1;
Enddecay
CDecay B_c-sig
#
Decay MyTau+
  1.00              TAUOLA 8; 
Enddecay
CDecay MyTau-
#
Decay MyJpsi
  1.00000  mu+  mu- PHOTOS VLL ;
Enddecay
#
End
